text: Ilyinka () is a rural locality (a village) in Mansurovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 173 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Uchaly, 2 km from Mansurovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Ilyinka, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
